  Moved to stable on x86.

  01 Feb 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> memtest86+-1.0.ebuild:
  The ebuild now makes use of the mount-boot eclass.

  01 Feb 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> memtest86+-1.0.ebuild:
  Added support for the local 'serial' USE flag.

